title: I just
body:
kind of want everyone else to arrive at Winterfell and see Petyr Baelish sitting at the lord’s table with this smug smile on his face.  

Jon will be furious, then Sansa will remind him that he left her in charge, so why not have Littlefinger fill one of the seats in Jon’s absence?  Meanwhile, Varys and Tyrion suddenly become very quiet.

Then after Bran reveals some things that only team Targ knows, rattling everyone, Baelish whips off his face to reveal a grinning Arya…

And as everyone else is flipping out about someone wearing someone else’s face, Varys bursts into a happy dance because pour the arbor gold and bring out the confetti, he outlived his nemesis!
